id: chewbacca_encounter
title: Reunion with Chewbacca
background_prompt: Treehouse clearing with Chewbacca and young Tarri, dense jungle
  visible through gaps, warm lantern glow, dramatic shadows, intimate conversation
  setting, star wars universe
music: friendly_reunion_warm__emotional_reunion_music__to.mp3
dialogue:
- narrator: Chewbacca leads Kai-Tara to a quieter platform, away from curious eyes.
- character:
    id: chewbacca
    text: Treechoppaw has been taken by the dark one. My nephew... he was exploring
      the old paths.
    mood: worried
    image: char_chewbacca_encounter_chewbacca_worried_fierce_Wookiee_warrior_with_brown_fur__w_0.jpeg
- character:
    id: kai_tara
    text: The Shrine of Dagorr? I sensed that location. It's a Sith ritual site.
    mood: serious
    image: char_chewbacca_encounter_kai_tara_serious_human_female_Jedi_Knight__brown_hair_in__0.jpeg
- character:
    id: chewbacca
    text: Raawr! (The dark one - he wears red blades, speaks of ancient power)
    mood: angry
    image: char_chewbacca_encounter_chewbacca_angry_fierce_Wookiee_warrior_with_brown_fur__w_0.jpeg
- character:
    id: kai_tara
    text: A Sith acolyte. Dangerous, but not a Master. We can handle this.
    mood: confident
    image: char_chewbacca_encounter_kai_tara_confident_human_female_Jedi_Knight__brown_hair_in__0.jpeg
- character:
    id: tarri
    text: Please save my uncle! I'll do anything!
    mood: desperate
    image: char_chewbacca_encounter_tarri_desperate_young_Wookiee_cub_with_lighter_brown_fur_0.jpeg
- character:
    id: kai_tara
    text: Stay here, young one. I'll bring him back.
    mood: determined
    image: char_chewbacca_encounter_kai_tara_determined_human_female_Jedi_Knight__brown_hair_in__0.jpeg
choice:
- text: Go alone to maintain stealth
  next: dark_omen
- text: Take Boushh as backup
  next: Boushh_backup
background: bg_chewbacca_encounter_Treehouse_clearing_with_Chewbacca_and_young_Tarri__0.jpeg
